lenders.name: Cecil Bund Memorial Fund
lenders.loan_because:
This was a birthday gift given to me to be able to help someone in the Pilippines make a better life for themselves
I Joni, Cecil's widow, am inspired by the Kiva program and the letter just received.  Sadly, my husband passed away on 17 Feb 2011, but I am carrying on the tradition and I would really love to know how to get Kiva into the Island of Or Mindoro, a place where we have friends in Calapan, Victoria and Pinamalayan to name a few as we spent 18 months on that Island 21 years ago and would like to help our friends succeed there as well.  How can this be possible?  Joni
